:: start-campfire

The wanderer [[clears up|start-mid-cleanup]] their campfire.
<<run window.removeFromCamp("campfire")>>

:: start-tent

The wanderer [[clears up|start-mid-cleanup]] their tent.
<<run window.removeFromCamp("tent")>>

:: start-pack

The wanderer [[clears up|start-mid-cleanup]] their pack.
<<run window.removeFromCamp("pack")>>

:: start-neal
The wanderer pats Neal. 

[["good boy."|start-mid-cleanup]] the wanderer says warmly.
<<run window.removeFromCamp("neal")>>

